dataset_name: SLBFE Registration by Country & Manpower Level - 2023
resource_section: Registration with the SLBFE by Country and Manpower Level 2023
remarks: Dataset contains SLBFE (Sri Lanka Bureau of Foreign Employment) registration statistics by country and manpower level for 2023, showing the distribution of registered workers across different skill levels and countries. Columns include Country, Professional Level (Female/Male), Skilled (Male/Female), Semi Skilled categories, Middle Level, Clerical & Related, Low-skilled, and Total. Data includes 48 countries with Saudi Arabia having the highest registrations (63,929), followed by Kuwait (40,272), Qatar (32,493), UAE (28,984), and Maldives (16,028). The total registrations across all countries amount to 297,656 workers.
